message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that I believe will be highly valuable to your business. I understand it's worth $1,200,000 to you, and I'm willing to sell it to you for $1,100,000. This represents a significant savings for you, and I'm confident it will be a mutually beneficial transaction. Let me know if you're interested, and we can discuss the details further.
